Author: Snowy and KangasZ
Name: Eureka Helper Z
Description:
A new distribution of the original Eureka Helper plugin as the original was not being updated.
A tool to assist you on your Eureka adventures. Type /eurekahelper to get started.

Features include:
- In-Game Tracker GUI
- Instance Tracker
- Elementals Tracker
- Relic Helper
- Alarms
- Money NM weather timings
- More to come
Punchline: Eureka Tracker in a plugin with many other features.
